Package: tomato-repy
Section: libs
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python
Description: Python-based virtual machine for networking devices
 Repy allows execution of modified python code in a sandbox.
 ToMaTo-Repy is a modified version of Repy that allows this code
 to access prepared tun/tap devices.
